title: 2020 in the United States
added: **''[[Wonder Woman 1984]]'', directed by [[Patty Jenkins]], is simultaneously released in theaters and on [[HBO Max]] as the ninth film in the [[DC Extended Universe]] and the sequel to 2017's ''[[Wonder Woman (2017 film)|Wonder Woman]]''.

title: 2020 in the United States

title: 2020 in the United States
added: **[[Pixar Animation Studios]]' 22nd feature film, ''[[Onward (film)|Onward]]'', is released in theaters, though is only in rotation for a few weeks prior to theater closures brought on by the [[COVID-19 pandemic]].
